    "description": "Get the protein hit you need with this classic kebab. You'll pan fry chicken before serving up with golden wedges and a creamy pumpkin seed salad. Drizzle the lot with garlic yoghurt and chilli sauce to finish. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
